## 9. Nginx Reverse Proxy Logic

Nginx decides where requests go:

- Static routing (path-based)
- FastCGI â†’ PHP (WordPress)
- Proxy â†’ HTTP services (cAdvisor)

Important:
- `location` priority matters
- Wrong order = WordPress hijacks everything

